-- UN May Complete Review of Hydro-Fluorocarbon Credits Methodology by August
-- Dinakar Sethuraman
-- 2010-06-22T01:19:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/un-may-complete-review-of-hydro-fluorocarbon-credits-methodology-by-august.html

          
          
             The United Nations may complete its
review on the methodology for awarding carbon credits for the
emission of hydro-fluorocarbon 23 gas by August, Clifford
Mahlung, chairman of the UN Clean Development Mechanism
executive board, said at the Carbon Markets Asia conference in
Singapore today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Dinakar Sethuraman in Singapore at 
 dinakar@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        